sequenceDiagram
    participant CF as Contact Form
    participant API as Express Server
    participant MW as Middleware
    participant CTR as Controller
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant ACT as Activity Logger
    participant DASH as Admin Dashboard

    Note over CF,DASH: PUBLIC ROUTE - Contact Form Submission
    CF->>API: POST /api/clients/contact
    API->>MW: Validate Request (JOI)
    MW->>CTR: clientController.submitContact()
    CTR->>DB: Create Client Document
    DB-->>CTR: Client Created
    CTR->>ACT: Log Activity (New Client)
    ACT->>DB: Save Activity
    DB-->>ACT: Activity Saved
    CTR-->>CF: 201 Success Response
    
    Note over CF,DASH: PROTECTED ROUTE - Admin Login
    DASH->>API: POST /api/auth/login {email, password}
    API->>MW: Validate Credentials (JOI)
    MW->>CTR: authController.login()
    CTR->>DB: Find Admin + Verify Password
    DB-->>CTR: Admin Found
    CTR->>CTR: Generate JWT Token
    CTR-->>DASH: 200 {token, admin}
    DASH->>DASH: Store Token in Memory/Context

    Note over CF,DASH: PROTECTED ROUTE - Fetch Dashboard Data
    DASH->>API: GET /api/dashboard/overview<br/>Header: Authorization Bearer {token}
    API->>MW: Auth Middleware (Verify JWT)
    MW->>MW: Decode Token & Find Admin
    MW->>CTR: dashboardController.getOverview()
    CTR->>DB: Aggregate Statistics
    DB-->>CTR: Stats Data
    CTR->>DB: Fetch Recent Clients
    DB-->>CTR: Recent Clients
    CTR->>DB: Fetch Recent Activities
    DB-->>CTR: Recent Activities
    CTR-->>DASH: 200 {stats, clients, activities}

    Note over CF,DASH: PROTECTED ROUTE - Create Project
    DASH->>API: POST /api/projects<br/>Header: Authorization Bearer {token}
    API->>MW: Auth Middleware
    MW->>MW: Validate Project Data (JOI)
    MW->>CTR: projectController.createProject()
    CTR->>DB: Verify Client Exists
    DB-->>CTR: Client Found
    CTR->>DB: Create Project
    DB-->>CTR: Project Created
    CTR->>ACT: Log Activity (New Project)
    ACT->>DB: Save Activity
    CTR-->>DASH: 201 {project}

    Note over CF,DASH: PROTECTED ROUTE - Update Project Status
    DASH->>API: PUT /api/projects/:id<br/>Header: Authorization Bearer {token}
    API->>MW: Auth Middleware
    MW->>CTR: projectController.updateProject()
    CTR->>DB: Find & Update Project
    DB-->>CTR: Project Updated
    CTR->>CTR: Check Status Change
    CTR->>ACT: Log Activity (Status Change)
    CTR->>CTR: Check Payment Status
    alt Payment Completed
        CTR->>ACT: Log Activity (Payment Received)
    end
    CTR-->>DASH: 200 {project}